<template>
  <vue-cal
  :time="false"
  hide-weekends 
  :disable-views="disable_views"
  :time-from="time_from"
  :time-to="time_to"
  :time-step="time_step"
  
  />
</template>


<script>

import VueCal from 'vue-cal'
import 'vue-cal/dist/vuecal.css'

export default {
  name: 'YourComponent',
  components: {
    VueCal,
  },
  data() {
    return {
        
        // disabling 
        disable_views : ['years', 'year'],
        disable_days : [], // 이거 computed로 설정. 곡 넣을 때 
        // week / day time interval
        time_from :"8 * 60",
        time_to :"19 * 60",
        time_step : "30",
      
    };
  },
};
</script>
